{
  "stem": "894.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And somehow, I didn't know how and when, but you did have that feeling that it's a matter of time, and that I'll be free.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In other words, I was never despondent to the point where I said, well, I'm going to die tomorrow.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I just-- somehow, when you're that young, I guess, you have the confidence that you're going to make it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was in the summer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because we arrived to Auschwitz sometimes in May, and that was six weeks later.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was not easy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was these-- you know, like you can visualize today, the slot machines, you know, where they have this arm?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You had to keep pulling this arm down.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was very hot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the steel pieces, you know, had to-- it made a hole or whatever other shapes that you made.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that was-- it was very, very difficult.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "At 12 o'clock at night, they gave us half an hour for eating lunch.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I remember laying down on the floor and rather sleeping than eating.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And at one point, I remember, a German came over.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he just kicked me with  a foot that it's time to get up.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I mean, not kick me hard, but just letting me know it's time to get up and-- and go to work.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I had a few experiences there that were interesting.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "One woman-- a German woman-- I can't recall the first meeting in camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But she took a liking to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And she would come to visit me every time she had a day off.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And she would bring her friends.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I cannot figure out whether she might have had a child that she missed or lost or what-- what her background was.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
